{"tid":2422380,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"BNO最後免稅買樓機會！英國據報擬延長印花稅豁免期至6月底！","createTime":"2021-02-25T06:57:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T10:02:23.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4e070ffc65afd2d449cbf138a409b9e7afeeb33b","tid":2422380,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T06:57:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://london.ac.uk/sites/default/files/styles/max_1300x1300/public/2018-10/london-aerial-cityscape-river-thames_1.jpg?itok=6LenFxuz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flondon.ac.uk%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fmax_1300x1300%2Fpublic%2F2018-10%2Flondon-aerial-cityscape-river-thames_1.jpg%3Fitok%3D6LenFxuz&h=fc96cb7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&lt;匯港通訊&gt; 英國1月底正式向港人開放 BNO 居留(Hong Kong BNO Visa)「5+1」簽證申請,令到不少港人移民時都會考慮購入英國物業。<br />\n<br />\n英國政府因新冠肺炎疫情推出「印花稅假期」(stamp duty holiday)的救市措施,原定3月結束。據《英國傳媒》報道,英國政府擬繼續延長至6月底。<br />\n<br />\n《每日電訊報》上周表示,財相辛偉誠正考慮「印花稅假期」延長6星期直至5月中旬,以防成千上萬的民眾因疫情拖慢交易進度,而無法受惠。<br />\n<br />\n但《泰晤士報》周三引述消息人士報道,辛偉誠將準備把印花稅假期延至6月底結束。他認為此舉有助振興房地產市場,協助英國經濟從封城政策中復甦。 (BC)"},{"pid":"1d209290de358a78b49c0105f4d978fed090371f","tid":2422380,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T14:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7867d52d69b6a5584d3c82af802382333a84f249","tid":2422380,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T10:02:23.000Z","msg":"[戇鳩警報器: 黃世澤 | martin oei | 交加街38號 ] 警世 黃世澤係令大家用唔到BNO移民既始作俑者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2423877\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2423877</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}